creator: SuperPOG
descriptionHtml:
The game is all about interaction, geared towards playing with your friends, colleagues, and the wider community.

Compete in leaderboards with other players from all around the world, earn points for picking the winning team, gain bonus points for guessing the correct score and earn streaks.

The closer your predictions are the better your game difference will be which increases your chances of winning.

Join the rest of our players and start making predictions right now. Sign up is quick and easy using Facebook or Google.
